Class Terminal

  • java.lang.Object
    • swp_compiler_ss13.fuc.parser.grammar.Symbol
      • swp_compiler_ss13.fuc.parser.grammar.Terminal
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Terminal.SpecialTerminal

    public class Terminal
extends Symbol
    Like all Symbols Terminals are identified by their String id, except Terminal.SpecialTerminal! They are identified by identity in memory and thus must be referenced from this class, like Epsilon or EOF.
